snippet.title: Circus Of TimTim - Console Release Announcement Trailer (PS4, PS5, XBOX)
snippet.description:
Our second console game is now announced! Circus of TimTim is coming to Playstation and XBOX. Finally, we made it .. :')

WISHLIST IT On Playstation ►►  Store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011415

WISHLIST IT On XBOX ►► LINK COMING SOON

Release Date: 26-07-2024

Circus of TimTim is a Stealth Horror Survival Game about two siblings trying to sneak inside the most hunted carnival of all time to recover lost items with a metal detector device, however enemies are roaming around and they can hear your every step! TimTim is not happy ..

Thanks so much for your support, really appreciate it!
